quran[8{c,v,t}:
12,79,"yousuf ne kaha"" panah ba khuda, dosray kisi shakhs ko hum kaisay rakh satke hain jis ke paas hum ne apna maal paaya hai is ko chore kar dosray ko rakhen ge to hum zalim hon ge """
12,80,"jab woh yousuf se mayoos ho gay to aik gooshay mein ja kar aapas mein mahswara karne lagey un mein jo sab se bara tha woh bola"" tum jantay nahi ho ke tumahray waalid tum se khuda ke naam par kya ehad o Paiman le chuke hain aur is se pehlay yousuf ke maamla mein jo zayad-ti tum kar chuke ho woh bhi tum ko maloom hai ab mein to yahan se hargiz nah jaoon ga jab taq ke mere waalid mujhe ijazat nah den, ya phir Allah hi mere haq mein koi faisla farma day ke woh sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai"
12,81,"tum ja kar apne waalid se kaho ke"" abba jaan, aap ke sahibzaday ne chori ki hai hum ne usay chori karte hue nahi dekha, jo kuch hamein maloom howa hai bas wohi hum bayan kar rahay hain, aur ghaib ki nigehbani to hum nah kar satke thay"
12,82,"aap uss bastii ke logon se pooch lijiye jahan hum thay uss qaafley se daryaft kar lijiye jis ke sath hum aeye hain hum apne bayan mein bilkul sachey hain """
12,83,"baap ne yeh daastaa’n sun kar kaha"" darasal tumahray nafs ne tumahray liye aik aur barri baat ko sahal bana diya acha is par bhi sabr karoon ga aur bakhoobi karoon ga kya baeed hai ke Allah un sab ko mujh se laa mila ye, woh sab kuch jaanta hai aur is ke sab kaam hikmat par mabni hain """
12,84,"phir woh un ki taraf se mun phair kar baith gaya aur kehnay laga ke"" ha ye Yousuf !"" woh dil hi dil mein gham se ghata ja raha tha aur is ki ankhen safaid par gayi theen"
12,85,"beton ne kaha"" khudaaraa! aap to bas Yousuf hi ko yaad kiye jatay hain nobat yeh aa gayi hai ke is ke gham mein apne aap ko ghulla den ge ya apni jaan halaak kar dalain ge """
12,86,"uss ne kaha"" mein apni pareshani aur apne gham ki faryaad Allah ke siwa kisi se nahi karta, aur Allah se jaissa mein waaqif hon tum nahi ho"
